items.name: opnsense-gateway-healthcheck
items.description: A Python-based Flask application to monitor the health of gateways in an OPNsense network. The application provides endpoints to check the health status of all gateways, specific gateways by name or address, and lists of healthy or unhealthy gateways. These gateways can include both internet service provider (ISP) and VPN-based gateways.
